@0 = ~You look like the kind o' person who knows how to live in the shadows.~
@1 = ~NP: And what of it?~ /*What did that do?*/
@2 = ~I take offense to that.~
@3 = ~NP: Why did you talk to me?~ /*Why are you telling me this?*/
@4 = ~NP: I'm just the kind of guy you need! I got a product that's gonna make your life a lot easier.~ /*In that case, I'm yer go-to guy! I've got the goods to make yer life easier.*/
@5 = ~I would like to see what you have to offer.~
@6 = ~I'd like to ask you some questions.~
@7 = ~No, thanks.~
@8 = ~Sorry <PRO_SIRMAAM>. My mistake. Won't bother ya no more then.~
@9 = ~Just step o'er here into the shadows and I'll show ya.~
@10 = ~Well, I'll tell ya what I can.~
@11 = ~What's going on here?~
@12 = ~I need some directions.~
@13 = ~Goodbye.~
@14 = ~Y'ever need something, ya just come to ol' Slider here. I'll take care o' ya.~
@15 = ~It's a mighty fine time fer folk like us. My business hasn't been this good in years, and in a town like Luskan, it's usually pretty good.~
@16 = ~What do you mean?~
@17 = ~What do I look like, a bleedin' map or somethin'? I've got customers waitin' on some special goods, so are ya gonna place an order or not?~
@18 = ~With the fighting between the High Captains, my business has been busier than ever. I sell to both sides and nobody'll touch me, 'cause they need my goods.~
@19 = ~How long has this been going on?~
@20 = ~Several weeks ago things got much more interesting 'round here. I've been raking in the gold since then. But look, I have other customers, so are ya plannin' to buy or not?~ /*Several weeks ago things got much more interesting 'round here. I've been raking in the gold since then.*/
@21 = ~NP: Don't turn your back on people again. There'll be people here who'll want to stab you in the back.~ /*Watch yer back 'round here <PRO_GIRLBOY>. There's lots o' folks liable to stick a knife in it.*/
